msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/command-line-interface.md:56
msgid "The command help is displayed using the system pager.  Hit the letter `q` to leave the pager.  `SPACE` scrolls one page down, cursor-down or `j` scrolls one line down, cursor-up or `k` scrolls one line up, `h` shows more help."
