#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:6
msgctxt "description"
msgid "Complete List Of Configuration Variables"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:13
msgid "The following configuration variables from the file `P:_config.yml` are understood by Qgoda:"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:15
msgid ""
"<ul>\n"
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"case-sensitive\" type='0 or 1' \n"
"   default='0' -%]\n"
"Set to 0 if you want to ignore case of filenames, 1 otherwise.  It is probably wise to keep the default value of 0 even on a case-sensitive file system.  Otherwise, you may run into problems, when you copy the site on another machine or some storage medium such as a USB stick.\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:22
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"exclude\" type='Array' \n"
"   default='empty' -%]\n"
"A list of files and directories that should not be processed.  Patterns are allowed.  See <a href=\"[% q.llink(name = 'excluding-files') %]\">[% q.lxref('title', name = 'excluding-files') %]</a>!\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:28
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"exclude_watch\" type='Array' \n"
"   default='same as \"exclude\" above' -%]\n"
"A list of files and directories that should not trigger a rebuild, when they change.  Patterns are allowed.  See <a href=\"[% q.llink(name = 'excluding-files') %]\">[% q.lxref('title', name = 'excluding-files') %]</a>!\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:34
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"linguas\" type='Array' \n"
"   default='undefined' -%]\n"
"A list of language codes for your site like \"en\", \"fr\", and so on.  It is recommended that you use <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3066\">HTTP language identifiers</a>.\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:40
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"link_score\" type='Integer' \n"
"   default=5 -%]\n"
"The relation score that two documents that have a link between each other get.  Note that this is counted from each document's side.  So, if document A links to B and B links to A, the overall relation score between A and B is 10.\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:46
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"no_scm\" type='List of patterns' \n"
"   default='none' -%]\n"
"A list of file name patterns that should be processed although not being under version control.  This only makes sense in conjunction with <code>C:scm</code>.\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:52
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"title\" type='String' \n"
"   default='\"A New Qgoda Powered Site\"' -%]\n"
"The name of the site.  Qgoda itself does not use this variable.\n"
"[%- END %]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/configuration-variables.md:58
msgid ""
"[% WRAPPER components/variable.html\n"
"   variable=\"po\" type='Hash' \n"
