#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:144
msgid "### Exclusion and Inclusion Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:146
msgid "Search patterns behave slightly different, when they are used for *excluding* files (as opposed to including files).  With pattern lists used for excluding files, you cannot re-include files or directories, when one of their parent directories is already excluded."
