#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:175
msgid "## Slashes"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:177
msgid "### Leading Slashes"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:179
msgid "A leading slash anchors the pattern to the source directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/pattern-lists.md:191
msgid "The first patterns starts with a slash.  It therefore excludes the top-level file `package.json` but it would not exclude `a/b/c/package.json`."
