"#: ../_views/partials/body.html:4\n"
"msgid \"Hello, world!\"\n"
"msgstr \"Hallo, Welt!\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:274
msgid "The string after `msgstr` is the translation. Try to translate at least one\n"
"string that is easy to recognize, when you rebuild your site."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:277
msgid "### Compile the `.po` Files"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:279
msgid ""
"The `.po` files are not immediately used for looking up translations but are\n"
"compiled into binary `.mo` files. The compilation also checks the `.po` file\n"
"for syntax errors and semantic errors."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:283
msgid "You can perform this step with `qgoda po mo`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:285
msgid ""
"```bash;line-numbers\n"
"$ qgoda po update-mo\n"
"[info][config] reading configuration from '_config.yaml'\n"
"[info] execute: msgfmt --check --statistics --verbose -o de.gmo de.po\n"
"de.po:7: warning: header field 'Project-Id-Version' still has the initial default value\n"
"de.po: 1 translated message.\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:293
msgid "You can fix the warning (line 4) by editing the first entry of the `.po`\n"
"file and fill in the missing information."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:296
msgid "In the last line you will see statistics about your translations, in particular\n"
"the number of translated and untranslated strings and fuzzy translations."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:299
msgid ""
"[@ WRAPPER components/infobox.html\n"
"           type='info' title='Fuzzy Translations' @]\n"
"Fuzzy translations are translations that have been automatically created\n"
"by <code>msgmerge</code> but have to be reviewed by a human. These translations\n"
"are *not* used until the fuzzy mark is removed from them. See the documentation\n"
"of your PO editor for more information.\n"
"[@ END @]"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:307
msgid "### Install the Translations"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:309
msgid "The last step is to install and use the translation:"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:311
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"$ qgoda po install\n"
"[info][config] reading configuration from '_config.yaml'\n"
"[info] create directory “/path/to/your/site/LocaleData/de/LC_MESSAGES”\n"
"[info] copy “de.gmo” to “/path/to/your/site/LocaleData/de/LC_MESSAGES/com.example.www.mo”\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:318
msgid ""
"The directory `P:LocaleData` contains the compiled translations. You should\n"
"add it to the [files to be excluded]([@ q.lanchor(name='excluding-files') @]) by\n"
"Qgoda."
msgstr ""

#: ../en/docs/translation-workflow.md:322
msgid ""
"The next time you rebuild your site with `qgoda watch` or `qgoda build`\n"
"the translated strings should be visible in their respective document\n"
"versions."
